# Title: File Decryption Using Gpg4win
# Author: Nasreddine Bencherchali (Nextron Systems)
# Date: 2023-08-09
# Level: medium
# Description: Detects usage of Gpg4win to decrypt files
# MITRE Tactic: Execution
# Tags: attack.execution
# Reference: https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma/blob/master/rules/windows/process_creation/proc_creation_win_gpg4win_decryption.yml

CommandLine="* -d *" CommandLine="*passphrase*" Image IN ("*\\gpg.exe", "*\\gpg2.exe") OR Description="GnuPG’s OpenPGP tool"